Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Airlines back Laker
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bv5h
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 Oct 1978
US airline chiefs back Sir Freddie Laker. Cheap flights have boosted industry-wide sales. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less